{
  "stem": "12413.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Everyone [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] was supposed to step out and to walk about five meters for evaluation.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And he was limping.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So he wanted to have a good view on the person.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Meanwhile, there were screams [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] not real far away from adjacent buildings.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And objects were flowing-- or dropping from the roofs.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "You have some, you know, house with three, four floors.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I think the Lithuanian and the Latvian were throwing babies in-- in the street.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "We heard shots.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Probably they were killing people who refused maybe to leave the houses.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "But we didn't pay attention, because I think we are paralyzed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "This was a completely kind of terror when you-- when you just-- your mind stops to think, and you turn just to listen, and to obey to orders.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And I went first.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I was tall.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "I was blonde blue eyes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "This would explain to you when I started walking, he looked at me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "But he look at me in way like I was looking straight into his eyes.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And he look at me with a kind of astonishment.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Later, I had a very close encounter with him, which I will talk about this later.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He asked me, what's your profession?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I say, I am a gardener, which was-- it was really immature.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I went to school before in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we did some farming and-- and gardening.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I have an [NON-ENGLISH]-- a certificate-- which said gardener.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He just gave a  half smile.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What kind of profession is that?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he sent me to the right, which means for life.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then went my brother.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He passed.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father-- he was scared to death.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I recall this.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was pale.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
